title: Brand New! Fine Shopping At Your Fingertips, Downtown Views! Gated
posting_body: ['Live an unparalleled lifestyle that blends leisure with convenience in the heart of Fort Worth, Texas.', 'Adjacent to the Chisholm Trail Parkway.', ' Easy access to Downtown Fort Worth, the Hospital District, Texas Christian University and the Fort Worth Cultural District.', ' We have mix of living options - from townhomes and urban studio efficiency apartments to loft apartments.', 'This rental community features poolside grilling and entertainment areas, a well-equipped fitness center, with yoga room and Private terrace lounge featuring striking views of Downtown Fort Worth and the Trinity Trails.', 'Convenient access to over 40 miles of hike-and-bike trails along the Trinity River.', 'Residents will enjoy the high-end specialty stores and distinctive restaurants of The Shops at Clearfork and Neiman Marcus opening February 2017 that are only a few steps away.', 'Please Call Desiree', 'show contact info', 'Mention Ad 405']
